data.description: Offers due Monday at noon.  Beautiful SF home in Wellington Valley stands ready for you!Gorgeous 3 bdrm & 3 full baths split level with attached garage!  Wonderfully adorned with brand new amenities such as new windows, new refrigerator, new high end air fryer range, new granite, new paint, new lighting, new carpet, natural gas generator, the list goes on & on! Cozy & welcoming recreation room complete with gas fireplace and walk-up to rear yard!  Warm gas heat & gas water heater with added rough in for future gas stove.  Super sized rear deck perfect for grilling & entertaining for the entire family and all the friends!  Nothing to do but move right in so don't delay see me today!🏡✨
